#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.128"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.128:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.128:0.2"
msgid "13. Bhayavagga"
msgstr "13. Fears"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.128:0.3"
msgid "128. Dutiyatathāgataacchariyasutta"
msgstr "128. Incredible Things About the Realized One (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.128:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Tathāgatassa, bhikkhave, arahato sammāsambuddhassa pātubhāvā cattāro "
"acchariyā abbhutā dhammā pātubhavanti."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, with the appearance of a Realized One, the perfected one, the "
"fully awakened Buddha, four incredible and amazing things appear."

msgctxt "an4.128:1.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro?"
msgstr "What four?"

#. VAR: Ālayārāmā → ālayarāmā (pts1)
msgctxt "an4.128:1.3"
msgid "Ālayārāmā, bhikkhave, pajā ālayaratā ālayasammuditā;"
msgstr "People like attachment, they love it and enjoy it."

msgctxt "an4.128:1.4"
msgid ""
"sā tathāgatena anālaye dhamme desiyamāne sussūsati sotaṃ odahati aññā cittaṃ "
"upaṭṭhapeti."
msgstr ""
"Yet when a Realized One is teaching the Dhamma of non-attachment, they want "
"to listen, they lend an ear, and they apply their minds to understand it."

msgctxt "an4.128:1.5"
msgid ""
"Tathāgatassa, bhikkhave, arahato sammāsambuddhassa pātubhāvā ayaṃ paṭhamo "
"acchariyo abbhuto dhammo pātubhavati."
msgstr ""
"This is the first incredible and amazing thing that appears with the "
"appearance of a Realized One."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.132"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.128:2.1"
msgid "Mānārāmā, bhikkhave, pajā mānaratā mānasammuditā."
msgstr "People like conceit, they love it and enjoy it."

msgctxt "an4.128:2.2"
msgid ""
"Sā tathāgatena mānavinaye dhamme desiyamāne sussūsati sotaṃ odahati aññā "
"cittaṃ upaṭṭhapeti."
msgstr ""
"Yet when a Realized One is teaching the Dhamma of removing conceit, they "
"want to listen, they lend an ear, and they apply their minds to understand "
"it."

msgctxt "an4.128:2.3"
msgid ""
"Tathāgatassa, bhikkhave, arahato sammāsambuddhassa pātubhāvā ayaṃ dutiyo "
"acchariyo abbhuto dhammo pātubhavati."
msgstr ""
"This is the second incredible and amazing thing that appears with the "
"appearance of a Realized One."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.128:3.1"
msgid "Anupasamārāmā, bhikkhave, pajā anupasamaratā anupasamasammuditā."
msgstr "People like excitement, they love it and enjoy it."

msgctxt "an4.128:3.2"
msgid ""
"Sā tathāgatena opasamike dhamme desiyamāne sussūsati sotaṃ odahati aññā "
"cittaṃ upaṭṭhapeti."
msgstr ""
"Yet when a Realized One is teaching the Dhamma of peace, they want to "
"listen, they lend an ear, and they apply their minds to understand it."

msgctxt "an4.128:3.3"
msgid ""
"Tathāgatassa, bhikkhave, arahato sammāsambuddhassa pātubhāvā ayaṃ tatiyo "
"acchariyo abbhuto dhammo pātubhavati."
msgstr ""
"This is the third incredible and amazing thing that appears with the "
"appearance of a Realized One."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an4.128:4.1"
msgid "Avijjāgatā, bhikkhave, pajā aṇḍabhūtā pariyonaddhā."
msgstr "This population is lost in ignorance, trapped in their shells."

msgctxt "an4.128:4.2"
msgid ""
"Sā tathāgatena avijjāvinaye dhamme desiyamāne sussūsati sotaṃ odahati aññā "
"cittaṃ upaṭṭhapeti."
msgstr ""
"Yet when a Realized One is teaching the Dhamma of removing ignorance, they "
"want to listen, they lend an ear, and they apply their minds to understand "
"it."

msgctxt "an4.128:4.3"
msgid ""
"Tathāgatassa, bhikkhave, arahato sammāsambuddhassa pātubhāvā ayaṃ catuttho "
"acchariyo abbhuto dhammo pātubhavati."
msgstr ""
"This is the fourth incredible and amazing thing that appears with the "
"appearance of a Realized One."

msgctxt "an4.128:4.4"
msgid ""
"Tathāgatassa, bhikkhave, arahato sammāsambuddhassa pātubhāvā ime cattāro "
"acchariyā abbhutā dhammā pātubhavantī”ti."
msgstr ""
"With the appearance of a Realized One, the perfected one, the fully awakened "
"Buddha, four incredible and amazing things appear.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.128:4.5"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
